    <body>
        <%- include('partials/header') %>

        <main>
            <section id="support-us" class="support-us-section">
                <div class="container">
                    <h1>Support Our Mission</h1>
                    <div class="support-content">
                        <p class="lead">Your generosity fuels our commitment to excellence in education at Pearlworth Foundation School.</p>
                        <p>Every donation, regardless of size, directly contributes to enhancing our students' learning experience and shaping their future. Your support enables us to:</p>
                        <ul class="support-list">
                            <li>Modernize our classrooms with cutting-edge technology</li>
                            <li>Expand our library with diverse educational resources</li>
                            <li>Upgrade sports facilities and equipment</li>
                            <li>Provide scholarships to deserving students</li>
                            <li>Invest in professional development for our dedicated staff</li>
                        </ul>
                        <p>Join us in nurturing young minds and building a brighter tomorrow. Your support makes a lasting impact.</p>
                        <a href="#donate" class="donate-button">Make a Donation</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
        </main>

        <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
